            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " in just 6 months and cited drivers for almost 3,500 traffic violations. The message is clear: if you want to engage in street racing or any other kind of illegal activities, including ",
